      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>teriyaki sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min further or until the sauce has thickened and the prawns are cooked through – this is your<strong> king prawn & pepper teriyaki</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1657033397217-x200.jpg",
